@startgantt
printscale weekly
Print between 2025-08-30 and 2026-07-10
Project starts 2025-09-01

-- Planning & Initiation --
[Project Kickoff] starts 2025-09-01 and lasts 3 days
[Stakeholder Identification] starts after [Project Kickoff]'s end and lasts 4 days
[High-level Scope Definition] starts after [Stakeholder Identification]'s end and lasts 5 days
[Feasibility and Risk Assessment] starts after [High-level Scope Definition]'s end and lasts 5 days
[Project Plan and Schedule] starts after [Feasibility and Risk Assessment]'s end and lasts 5 days
[Planning Complete] happens at [Project Plan and Schedule]'s end

-- Requirements --
[Requirements Workshops] starts after [Planning Complete]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Use Cases and User Stories] starts after [Requirements Workshops]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Draft SRS] starts after [Use Cases and User Stories]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Requirements Review] starts after [Draft SRS]'s end and lasts 4 days
[Requirements Baseline] happens at [Requirements Review]'s end

-- Design --
[High-level Architecture] starts after [Requirements Baseline]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Database and API Design] starts after [High-level Architecture]'s end and lasts 10 days
[UI and UX Wireframes] starts after [High-level Architecture]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Detailed Design Spec] starts after [Database and API Design]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Design Review] starts after [Detailed Design Spec]'s end and lasts 4 days
[Design Sign-off] happens at [Design Review]'s end

-- Implementation --
[Dev Environment and CI Setup] starts after [Design Sign-off]'s end and lasts 5 days
[Core Backend Development] starts after [Dev Environment and CI Setup]'s end and lasts 20 days
[Core Frontend Development] starts after [Dev Environment and CI Setup]'s end and lasts 20 days
[Integration Development] starts after [Core Backend Development]'s end and lasts 15 days
[Code Review and Refactor] starts after [Integration Development]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Code Freeze] happens at [Code Review and Refactor]'s end

-- Testing --
[Unit and Integration Testing] starts after [Code Freeze]'s end and lasts 15 days
[System and Regression Testing] starts after [Unit and Integration Testing]'s end and lasts 15 days
[Performance and Security Testing] starts after [System and Regression Testing]'s end and lasts 10 days
[User Acceptance Testing] starts after [Performance and Security Testing]'s end and lasts 10 days
[Test Sign-off] happens at [User Acceptance Testing]'s end

-- Pilot Release Preparation --
[Release Planning and Runbook] starts after [Test Sign-off]'s end and lasts 5 days
[Pilot Validation] starts after [Release Planning and Runbook]'s end and lasts 5 days
[Packaging and Controlled Handoff] starts after [Pilot Validation]'s end and lasts 4 days
[Pilot Release Ready] happens at [Packaging and Controlled Handoff]'s end

-- Post-Submission Stabilization --
[First Patch Release] happens on 14 days after [Pilot Release Ready]'s end
[Follow-up Fixes Iteration 1] starts after [Pilot Release Ready]'s end and lasts 15 days
[Follow-up Fixes Iteration 2] starts after [Follow-up Fixes Iteration 1]'s end and lasts 15 days
[Limited Maintenance Ongoing] starts after [Follow-up Fixes Iteration 2]'s end and lasts 40 days

@endgantt